## PriorityListGroupMap type

The `PriorityListGroupMap` is a map to map the (integer) priority to a \[\[PriorityListGroup\]\].

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type PriorityListGroupMap<T extends PriorityListElement> = Map<number, PriorityListGroup<T>>;
```
